    h2 Form Inputs Validation
    p Form validation is an important part of web development. This section will show you how to make this easy to change form input fields, label colors and adding some validation messages to the <code>.form__group</code>

  .md-col-6
    h2 Form Inputs Validation Colors


    p The form <code>.has__{identifier}</code>automatically changes colors of the child elements in the  <code>.form__group</code> block element.
    p Simply add <code>info</code> , <code>warning</code> , <code>success</code> or <code>danger</code> as the {identifier} to change the input and label colors.


  .md-col-6
    .well
      .form__group.has__info
        label.form__label Info Input
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
      .form__group.has__warning
        label.form__label Warning Input
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
      .form__group.has__success
        label.form__label Success Input
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
      .form__group.has__danger
        label.form__label Danger Input
        input(type="text", class="form__item")

  .md-col-12
    pre <code>&lt;div class=&quot;form__group has__info&quot;&gt;
      |    &lt;label class=&quot;form__label&quot;&gt;Info Input&lt;/label&gt;
      |    &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form__item&quot;&gt;
      |  &lt;/div&gt;
      |  &lt;div class=&quot;form__group has__warning&quot;&gt;
      |    &lt;label class=&quot;form__label&quot;&gt;Warning Input&lt;/label&gt;
