    </code>

  .md-col-6

    h2 Form Validation Messages

    p The validation message will inherit the color of the validation colors class above. Just add a <code>span</code> element with a class of <code>.form__helper</code> after the input field with in the <code>.form__group</code> block ether using php or JavaScript.

  .md-col-6
    .well
      .form__group.has__info
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
        span.form__helper Info Message
      .form__group.has__warning
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
        span.form__helper Warning Message
      .form__group.has__success
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
        span.form__helper Success Message
      .form__group.has__danger
        input(type="text", class="form__item")
        span.form__helper Error Message

  .md-col-12
    pre <code>&lt;div class=&quot;form__group has__info&quot;&gt;
      |    &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form__item&quot;&gt;
      |    &lt;span class=&quot;form__helper&quot;&gt;Info Message&lt;/span&gt;
      |  &lt;/div&gt;
