    h2 Form Input sizes
    p Just like the <code>.btn</code> element the form input field can be resized by using style modifyers like <code>.form__item--xs</code> <code>.form__item--sm</code> <code>.form__item--md</code> <code>.form__item--lg</code> <code>.form__item--xl</code>.

  .md-col-6
    .well
      .form__group
        input(type="text", placeholder="Extra small - xs", class="form__item form__item--xs")
      .form__group
        input(type="text", placeholder="Small - sm", class="form__item form__item--sm")
      .form__group
        input(type="text", placeholder="Medium - xs", class="form__item form__item--md")
      .form__group
        input(type="text", placeholder="Large - lg", class="form__item form__item--lg")
      .form__group
        input(type="text", placeholder="Extra Large - xl", class="form__item form__item--xl")

  .md-col-12
    pre <code>&lt;div class=&quot;form__group&quot;&gt;
