  .md-col-6

    h2 Horizontal Form
    p The <strong>horizontal</strong> style form can be created by using the <strong>grid classes</strong> and adding <code>.form__horizontal</code> to the parent container.
  .md-col-6
    .well
      form(action="", method="post", class="form__horizontal")
        .form__group
          label(for="name", class="md-col-3 md-text-align-right form__label") Name
          .md-col-9
            input(type="text" class="form__item", id="name")

        .form__group
          label(for="email", class="md-col-3 md-text-align-right form__label") Email
          .md-col-9
            input(type="email" class="form__item", id="email")
        .form__group
          label(for="content", class="md-col-3 md-text-align-right form__label") Content
          .md-col-9
            textarea(class="form__item", id="content")

        .form__group
          .md-col-9.md-offset-3
            button(class="btn btn--primary") Submit
            button(class="btn") Learn more

